## Station

### 역 추가
POST http://localhost:8080/stations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lineName": "2호선",
  "currentStationName": "F",
  "nextStationName": "K",
  "distance": 6
}

### 역 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/stations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lineName": "2호선",
  "stationName": "F"
}

